title: I Reincarnated As a Girl in Another World, but It Was Okay Because I Was Together With a Girl - Novel Updates
tags: Male to Female   Reincarnated in Another World
author: 超三元豚
description:
Subaru Yuuki, a peaceful high school otaku boy, with social anxiety disorder.

Reincarnated in another world with ambiguous memories.

While thinking this, he reincarnated as a girl.

Looks of a girl. Brains of a boy.

It is such a story.>
